queries.sql: SELECT *,(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM ref_klaim as it WHERE it.idcpmk = mk_klaim_detail.idcpmk) as entry_count FROM mk_klaim_header left join mk_klaim_detail on mk_klaim_header.idklaim=mk_klaim_detail.idklaim LEFT JOIN ref_klaim on mk_klaim_header.idklaim=ref_klaim.idklaim and mk_klaim_detail.idcpmk=ref_klaim.idcpmk LEFT JOIN dok_portofolio on ref_klaim.no_dokumen= dok_portofolio.no_dokumen WHERE mk_klaim_header.no_peserta = '12023-0001' order by mk_klaim_header.nama_matakuliah,mk_klaim_detail.idcpmk
